{"tid":581461,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"以後可以唔使去OK","createTime":"2018-03-05T11:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T14:20:48.000Z","uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"046532d8830d351a7457741cf6532f8ebbbe3d43","tid":581461,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T11:09:05.000Z","msg":"長者只要在首階段參與計劃，位於天水圍、上水、元朗、長洲及東涌，合共三十四間的OK便利店內，出示長者卡，即可在無須購物的情況下，以EPS會員銀行發出的銀行卡提款，金額由一百元為倍數起，每次最多提取五百元。每張銀行卡每日最多可使用服務兩次，持卡人毋須繳付任何交易費用，易辦事期望在年底前有更多便利店提供服務。(資料由商業電台提供)<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/28871158_10155409297097081_2522572871464102388_n.png?oh=bb7d693df4a4da0a5c7e8d9fe4e74c16&amp;oe=5B4E00E2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F28871158_10155409297097081_2522572871464102388_n.png%3Foh%3Dbb7d693df4a4da0a5c7e8d9fe4e74c16%26oe%3D5B4E00E2&h=f0a1b495&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e61ae283fc903f09d50dee938c08aa2c32c0247","tid":581461,"uid":103759,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"第時去OK 買嘢 前面隨時有個阿伯係前面不停打錯密碼 而你就俾唔到錢"},{"pid":"3c63331413de5aa88928e799650d733ae40d0145","tid":581461,"uid":41944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:20:48.000Z","msg":"廢老有幾可用EPS<br />\nATM 都唔識用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}